## ğŸ”§ Configuration

### Environment Variables

```bash
export GITHUB_TOKEN="your-github-token"
export ANSIBLE_HOST_KEY_CHECKING=False
export ANSIBLE_INVENTORY="inventories/production/hosts.yml"
```

### Inventory Example

```yaml
all:
  children:
    web_servers:
      hosts:
        web1:
          ansible_host: 10.0.1.10
          ansible_user: ubuntu
    database_servers:
      hosts:
        db1:
          ansible_host: 10.0.1.20
          ansible_user: ubuntu
```

